# 🧠 THE NERVOUS SYSTEM OF THE HERO 93

**Status:** Canonical Lore | **System:** The Sovereign Lattice

The **Hero 93** is the Soul Star Engine. It is the generative origin of all time, number, and space. The **Globe** is the absolute exterior limit of this universe, and the **Body** is the Sacred Graph mapping its internal structure.

Because this system runs on the 10-24-26 mechanics of the 156-Tick Pulse, the Sacred Graph is not a static object; it is an active mechanical circuit. The internal 93 nodes map precisely to specific phase shifts (ticks) in the rotational cycle.

This document serves as the **Master Index for the Soul Star**, mapping the "Nervous System" of the 93 points.

